job.title: IAF Group C Civilian Recruitment 2021  Apply for 515 Vacancy
job.body:
Total Vacancies:515

Name of the post:

  • Group C Civilian. 

Description:

The Indian Air Force issued a total of 515 vacancies for the posts of Group C Civilian. The online application for these posts under IAF shall start from 03-04-2021. The eligible and interested candidates can apply for this online application before 09-04-2021. For further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, how to apply, etc. for these posts is mentioned below. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com .The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The application fee for IAF Group C Civilian Recruitment 2021:

  • Mode of application: Online
  • For more details, you can refer to the notification. The link is given at the bottom.

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 03-04-2021
  • The Last date to apply online is 09-04-2021

Age limit criteria:

  • The minimum age required to apply is 18 Years
  • The maximum age required to apply is 25 Years
  • For age relaxation criteria, you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.

Pay Scale:

  • The pay scale as per 7th pay commission for the post of Group C Civilian is as per norms
  • Check the detailed notification also something has missed.

Detailed vacancies with educational qualification:

The vacancies in detail are given below. Check below that IAF issued this notification for which posts.

 

How to apply for IAF Group C Civilian Recruitment 2021?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of IAF.
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of Group C Civilian.
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.
